Wallace Weitz Buys The Procter & Gamble, Apollo Group Inc., Strayer Education Inc., Sells Avon Products Inc., Bed Bath & Beyond Inc., DR Pepper SnappleWallace Weitz Q2 Portfolio UpdateAugust 05, 2009 |  About: 
